	<h1 class="title">原来大众公司的美国主管早在 2014 年就知情“排放门”</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Danielle Ivory, Jack Ewing</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-10 08:00:34 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15846/medium/15846.jpg?1444377713" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


